dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4lin.lintopology

Interface ILinSlaveConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface ILinSlaveConfig
extends IEntity
    ILinSlaveConfig: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Node attributes of LIN slaves that are handled by the LinMaster. In the System Description LIN slaves may be described in the context of the Lin Master. In an ECU Extract of the LinMaster the LinSlave Ecus shall not be available. The information that is described here is necessary in the ECU Extract for the configuration of the LinMaster. The values of attributes of LinSlaveConfig and the corresponding LinSlave shall be identical (if both are defined in a System Description).

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
